		<title>狗狗超會聽聲音？牠的「條件反射」遠超人類想像！</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/12/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e8%b6%85%e6%9c%83%e8%81%bd%e8%81%b2%e9%9f%b3%ef%bc%9f%e7%89%a0%e7%9a%84%e3%80%8c%e6%a2%9d%e4%bb%b6%e5%8f%8d%e5%b0%84%e3%80%8d%e9%81%a0%e8%b6%85%e4%ba%ba%e9%a1%9e%e6%83%b3%e5%83%8f/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 12 Nov 2025 06:15:52 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
