		<title>貓咪也會「社交疲勞」？從這些行為變化看出牠的壓力信號 !</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/11/%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e4%b9%9f%e6%9c%83%e3%80%8c%e7%a4%be%e4%ba%a4%e7%96%b2%e5%8b%9e%e3%80%8d%ef%bc%9f%e5%be%9e%e9%80%99%e4%ba%9b%e8%a1%8c%e7%82%ba%e8%ae%8a%e5%8c%96%e7%9c%8b%e5%87%ba%e7%89%a0%e7%9a%84/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 11 Nov 2025 05:42:30 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
